WEBVTT

00:05:27.240 --> 00:05:33.480
I met around four to five hundred people

00:05:33.480 --> 00:05:37.760
who were close to 80, 90 
or 100 years of age.

00:05:37.760 --> 00:05:42.520
There was no internet
or mobile phones in those days.

00:05:42.520 --> 00:05:47.400
The wonderful thing that happened was 
that I spent time with them.

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:49.640
Today I am over 50,

00:05:49.640 --> 00:05:53.440
and the way my life has panned out 
and the way I have got here

00:05:53.440 --> 00:05:56.960
is thanks to what I heard from them.

00:05:56.960 --> 00:06:02.400
Today, with the way things are, 
we are so involved with technology